tr: "inna <strong>al</strong>l<u>aa</u>ha l<u>aa</u> yaghfiru an yusyraka bihi wayaghfiru m<u>aa</u> duuna <u>dzaa</u>lika liman yasy<u>aa</u>u waman yusyrik bi<strong>al</strong>l<u>aa</u>hi faqad <u>dh</u>alla <u>dh</u>al<u>aa</u>lan ba'iid<u>aa</u><strong>n</strong>",
